                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <add>י\"ד באייר התרי\"ך</add>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <date>May 19<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1857</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>My Dear Sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I expected ere this my last commu<lb/>nication would have appeared\n                in your periodical<lb/> as the one of the Jewish Chronicle which was <lb/>sent same\n                time after yours has already met<lb/> with attention. I am at a loss to know\n                the<lb/> cause as I replied to your note also relative<lb/> to my being appointed\n                your agent here and<lb/> my views thereon.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">There is nothing of importance<lb/> stirring here in Jewish matters,\n                the sister con<lb/>gregation is expecting the <persName>Revd Alexr B.\n                    Davis</persName><lb/> from <placeName>London</placeName>, lately of\n                    <placeName>Portsea, Portsmouth</placeName><lb/> to undertake the duties of the\n                ministry, he is<lb/> said to be in the expected packet due on <date>Sun<lb/>day the\n                        21<hi rend=\"sup\">st</hi></date>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">In my last letter I took the liber<lb/>ty of soliciting the aid of\n                your services to procure<lb/> for me a few books for which on my being<lb/>\n                acquainted with the cost I shall remit you the<lb/> money through a house in\n                    <placeName>New York</placeName>. Viz.<lb/>\n                <persName>Salomon's</persName> Lectures</p>\n            <p><persName>Dias's</persName> Letters in the evidences of Christianity 3 sets the<lb/>\n                Hebrew spelling Books 6 copies whole series in each <sic>sett</sic><lb/> Catechisms\n                for young children 6 <add>?</add></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I have sent you <del>a</del> newspaper<lb/> reports of my sermon on\n                    <add>שבת אמור</add> which you can<lb/> make use of, and as a friend and brother in<lb/>\n                <placeName>Israel</placeName>, should you know of any works calcula</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3fj29z9x/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
